    <title>使用 Hexo 和 GitHub 搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="https://github.com/newiflin/newiflin.github.io/2019/10/19/hexo-blog/"/>
    <id>https://github.com/newiflin/newiflin.github.io/2019/10/19/hexo-blog/</id>
    <published>2019-10-19T12:24:03.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-19T18:51:00.052Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><blockquote><p>老早就有写博客的念头，因各种原因推到现在。废话少说，就此开始搭建一个基于 Hexo 与 GitHub 的博客。</p></blockquote><h2 id="环境"><a href="#环境" class="headerlink" title="环境"></a>环境</h2><ul><li>node.js（推荐 10.0 版本及以上）</li><li>git</li><li>hexo</li></ul><hr><h2 id="Node-js"><a href="#Node-js" class="headerlink" title="Node.js"></a>Node.js</h2><h3 id="什么是Node-js"><a href="#什么是Node-js" class="headerlink" title="什么是Node.js"></a>什么是Node.js</h3><p><strong>Node.js</strong>  是一个基于 Chrome V8 引擎的JavaScript运行时环境，运行在服务端，且开源、跨平台。</p><p>Node.js大部分基本模块使用 JavaScript 编写，使用事件驱动、非阻塞和异步输入输出模型等技术提供性能。</p><h3 id="Node-js安装"><a href="#Node-js安装" class="headerlink" title="Node.js安装"></a>Node.js安装</h3><p>登录官网下载：<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/</a></p><p><img src="%5Cimages%5Chexo-blog%5Cnodejs-install.png" alt="Node.js的安装"></p><p>下载windows安装包，安装一路 next 即可。</p><p>查看是否安装成功，运行 <code>node -v</code>，出现版本号。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\Users\dell&gt;node -v</span><br><span class="line">v10.16.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更改npm源"><a href="#更改npm源" class="headerlink" title="更改npm源"></a>更改npm源</h3><p>查看npm源</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config get registry</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更换为国内镜像</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="git"><a href="#git" class="headerlink" title="git"></a>git</h2><h3 id="什么是git"><a href="#什么是git" class="headerlink" title="什么是git"></a>什么是git</h3><p>git是优秀的分布式版本控制系统。</p><h3 id="git的安装"><a href="#git的安装" class="headerlink" title="git的安装"></a>git的安装</h3><ul><li>windows安装，直接访问 <a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git官网下载</a>。根据电脑位数，选择32/64bit 对应安装即可。</li></ul><img src="C:\Users\dell\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\1571482067937.png" alt="1571482067937" style="zoom: 80%;" /><ul><li>打开 Git Bash 设置git用户名和邮箱</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --global user.name &quot;newiflin&quot;</span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.email &quot;newiflin@gmail.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="GitHub"><a href="#GitHub" class="headerlink" title="GitHub"></a>GitHub</h3><p>GitHub 是目前主流的开源代码托管平台，同时也是程序员的社交和学习平台。</p><ul><li><p>注册GitHub账号</p></li><li><p>创建一个私有仓库（私有仓库已免费，微软于去年收购GitHub）</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cdell%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1571485416693.png" alt="1571485416693"></p></li></ul><hr><h2 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h2><h3 id="什么是Hexo"><a href="#什么是Hexo" class="headerlink" title="什么是Hexo"></a>什么是Hexo</h3><p><strong>Hexo</strong> 是一个快速、简单和功能强大的博客框架，支持 markdown 等标记语言，可以立即生成带有优美主题的静态文件。</p><p>Hexo官方文档：<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/</a></p><h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><ul><li><p>安装Hexo之前，确保已经按照 <strong>Node.js</strong> 和 <strong>Git</strong></p></li><li><p>在H盘新建文件夹blog</p></li><li><p>cmd运行命令<code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code></p><p>报了两个错误，不过并不影响后续。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">H:\blog&gt;npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">C:\Users\dell\AppData\Roaming\npm\hexo -&gt; C:\Users\dell\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\hexo-cli\bin\hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: fsevents@2.1.1 (node_modules\hexo-cli\node_modules\fsevents):</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: Unsupported platform for fsevents@2.1.1: wanted &#123;&quot;os&quot;:&quot;darwin&quot;,&quot;arch&quot;:&quot;any&quot;&#125; (current: &#123;&quot;os&quot;:&quot;win32&quot;,&quot;arch&quot;:&quot;x64&quot;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>运行<code>hexo init newiflin.github.io</code>，创建博客目录</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">H:\blog&gt;git init newiflin.github.io</span><br><span class="line">H:\blog&gt;cd newiflin.github.io</span><br><span class="line">H:\blog\newiflin.github.io&gt;npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>启动hexo服务</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">H:\blog\hexo&gt;hexo s</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>启动Chrome，访问<a href="http://localhost:4000，预览页面" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000，预览页面</a></li></ul><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cdell%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1571480312115.png" alt="1571480312115"></p><ul><li>发表文章，命令<code>hexo new [文章名]</code></li></ul><p>会在source/_posts目录下生成对应的 md 文件，可预览页面。</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cdell%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1571488064048.png" alt="1571488064048"></p><ul><li><p>修改hexo目录下的 <strong>_config.yml</strong> 文件</p><ol><li><p>修改 deploy 部分</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/newiflin/hexo.github.io</span><br><span class="line">  branch: gh-pages</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改 url 和 root</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: https://github.com/newiflin/hexo</span><br><span class="line">root: /hexo/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>模板默认为 lanscape，可修改配置文件，更换主题</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: landscape</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li></ul><h3 id="静态文件生成"><a href="#静态文件生成" class="headerlink" title="静态文件生成"></a>静态文件生成</h3><p>修改博客或配置文件后，执行以下命令，生成静态网页。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>hexo generate</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">H:\blog\hexo&gt;npx hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Files loaded in 1.02 min</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/fancybox_loading.gif</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: archives/2019/10/index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/blank.gif</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: archives/index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/jquery.fancybox.css</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/fancybox_sprite.png</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/fancybox_overlay.png</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/fancybox_sprite@2x.png</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/fancybox_loading@2x.gif</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/helpers/jquery.fancybox-buttons.css</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: js/script.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/helpers/jquery.fancybox-thumbs.css</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/helpers/jquery.fancybox-media.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/helpers/jquery.fancybox-buttons.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/fonts/FontAwesome.otf</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: archives/2019/index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/helpers/fancybox_buttons.png</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.woff</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/style.css</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.svg</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/jquery.fancybox.pack.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.eot</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/helpers/jquery.fancybox-thumbs.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.ttf</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: css/images/banner.jpg</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: 2019/10/19/hello-world/index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: fancybox/jquery.fancybox.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  28 files generated in 4.18 s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署到服务器"><a href="#部署到服务器" class="headerlink" title="部署到服务器"></a>部署到服务器</h3><ul><li>确保已安装git部署器，未安装执行以下命令：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>部署到远程服务器</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>GitHub对应仓库的分支下，可查到提交的代码。</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5Cdell%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1571485524596.png" alt="1571485524596"></p><p>访问GitHub Page，即可浏览博客页，参考：<a href=""https://newiflin.github.io"">newiflin.github.io</a></p><p>至此，基于 hexo + GitHub 的博客就基本搭建完毕。</p><hr>]]></content>
    
